Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憧～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公交呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有3分鐘才到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  轉校生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是穿得這麼可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這在東京很流行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的愛好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在東京也是屬於極少數派的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  差不多請不要再用「轉校生」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有「可愛小姐」之類的稱呼可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那麼  叫你什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原村和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們成為朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
